doi: 10.5281/zenodo.18990235
url: https://github.com/opinionated-systems/markspace
abstract: >
  A stigmergic coordination protocol for LLM agent fleets.
  Enforces safety and coordination constraints in a deterministic
  guard layer outside the agents, so guarantees hold independent
  of agent behavior.
